per_sionl.overlap_ep_preT_tot - Population in extreme poor (<$1.25 a day) only receiving All Social Insurance (%, preT)
per_sionl.overlap_ep_tot - Population in extreme poor (<$1.25 a day) only receiving All Social Insurance (%)
per_sionl.overlap_pop_preT_tot - Population only receiving All Social Insurance (%, preT)
per_sionl.overlap_pop_rur - Population only receiving All Social Insurance (%) -rural
per_sionl.overlap_pop_tot - Population only receiving All Social Insurance (%)
per_sionl.overlap_pop_urb - Population only receiving All Social Insurance (%) -urban
per_sionl.overlap_q1_preT_tot - Population in the poorest quintile only receiving All Social Insurance (%, preT)
per_sionl.overlap_q1_rur - Population in the poorest quintile only receiving All Social Insurance (%) -rural
per_sionl.overlap_q1_tot - Population in the poorest quintile only receiving All Social Insurance (%)
per_sionl.overlap_q1_urb - Population in the poorest quintile only receiving All Social Insurance (%) -urban
PHOSROCK - Phosphate rock, $/mt, current$
PLATINUM - Platinum, $/toz, nominal$
